# Jenkins Task 2

## Objective

Automatically trigger a Jenkins build whenever code is pushed to GitHub and send the build notification via email.

## Tech Stack

- AWS EC2
- Docker
- Jenkins
- GitHub

## Steps Performed

1. Installed Jenkins on AWS EC2 using Docker.
2. Created a GitHub repository.
3. Added a shell script (build.sh).
4. Connected Jenkins with the GitHub repository.
5. Configured GitHub Webhook.
6. Enabled automatic build trigger on push.
7. Configured Gmail SMTP.
8. Configured Email Extension Plugin.
9. Verified successful build and email notification.

## Repository Used for Build

https://github.com/s1u2n3/jenkins_task_2

## Result

✔ Automatic build triggered after every commit.

✔ Email notification sent successfully.

